overview: The user initiated a review of their sleep questionnaire application,
  providing detailed specifications for its functionality, data collection, and
  reporting. The agent conducted a comprehensive analysis, identifying several
  missing features and areas for improvement. Following this, the agent began
  implementing the identified high-priority tasks. So far, the agent has
  successfully integrated a 1-10 tiredness severity scale with critical safety
  warnings, added logic for detecting and reporting Comorbid Insomnia and Sleep
  Apnea (COMISA), and implemented detection and recommendations for Insufficient
  Sleep Syndrome. Additionally, a new "Resources & Next Steps" section with
  relevant external links has been added to both the web and PDF reports. The
  agent is currently in the process of implementing weighted scoring for
  Excessive Daytime Sleepiness.
